metadata.name: PLAYPUS #01 DJ
metadata.description:
Playpus is a platypus looking for its own personality. Playpus loves dressing up as famous characters these days. In this collection, we will see playpus dressed as these famous people with beautiful costumes and I am sure we will want to buy them. Let's have fun with Playpus.

Playpus started out as the first DJ in disguise. This costume made him a fun personality.
